<body id="page-top">

    <header class="masthead text-center text-white d-flex">
      <div class="container my-auto">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-uppercase">
              <strong>歡迎Tapioca!</strong>
            </h1>
            <hr>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <p class="text-faded mb-5">這個網站是為了讓日本人和台灣人相互建立友誼所創造的。珍珠是很多日本人以及台灣人喜歡的食物，所以我們取這個名字。開始吧！</p>
            <%= link_to '註冊', new_user_registration_path , :class => "btn btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger mr-3" %>
            <%= link_to '登入' ,new_user_session_path, :class => "btn btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger ml-3" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="bg-primary" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-white">開始吧！</h2>
            <hr class="light my-4">
            <p class="text-faded mb-4">如果您現在開始使用，您就會遇到有很多不錯的交友機會。沒有猶豫的理由吧！</p>
            <%= link_to 'Get started!', new_user_registration_path , :class => "btn btn-light btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading">我們為您們提供的東西</h2>
            <hr class="my-4">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-diamond text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">堅強的網站</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">我們的網站會自動更新，所以不會當掉。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-paper-plane text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">聊天功能</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">您可以跟配對的朋友們聊天！</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-newspaper-o text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">更新</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">我們會更新依賴的關係以保持新鮮。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 text-center">
            <div class="service-box mt-5 mx-auto">
              <i class="fa fa-4x fa-heart text-primary mb-3 sr-icons"></i>
              <h3 class="mb-3">建立友誼</h3>
              <p class="text-muted mb-0">您使用這個網站之後您應該會有很多朋友！</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-dark text-white">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-4">開始吧!</h2>
        <%= link_to '註冊!', new_user_registration_path , :class => "btn btn-light btn-xl sr-button" %>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading">請聯絡我們!</h2>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <p class="mb-5">您準備好了嗎？讚！請給我們email或是電話。我們會盡量快速回覆！</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 ml-auto text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-phone fa-3x mb-3 sr-contact"></i>
            <p>123-456-6789</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 mr-auto text-center">
            <i class="fa fa-envelope-o fa-3x mb-3 sr-contact"></i>
            <p>
              <a href="mailto:your-email@your-domain.com">example@example.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
</body>